Volume Normalizer: How To Use

This program is intended to normalize the volume of a entire folder of CON files by modifying the DTA without modifying any audio.

This operation IS destructive in which your CON files will be changed. However, the only modifications will be to the volume levels.

OPTIONS
'Backup Original DTA' will create a copy of the songs DTA file in a folder called 'Backup DTA' in the same folder where the operation is ran. This option will NOT overwrite existing files discovered in that folder if there already exists a backup.